00:56:47.890 --> 00:56:50.010
to be "vacation" markets.

00:56:50.010 --> 00:56:52.430
But they're finding
enough demand for it.

00:56:52.430 --> 00:56:54.534
So it's really working
out well for most people.

00:56:54.534 --> 00:56:56.450
JORDAN THIBODEAU: Have
they had the strategies

00:56:56.450 --> 00:56:58.032
that have been proven fruitful?

00:56:58.032 --> 00:56:59.990
